{"tid":2142329,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果將漢文拉丁化嘅話","createTime":"2020-08-06T10:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T11:36:41.000Z","uid":363330,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6069fb02f0a3c6baa6cb8a2a7b5a617217613862","tid":2142329,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n見有人討論有關漢字拉丁化嘅嘢<br />\n講真現實可行程度都幾低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上亦有人講<br />\n不如直接用英文重實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n但作為一種想像好似都幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設一個異世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫Honkongia<br />\n使用一種叫Honkongish嘅語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先介紹一下Honkongish嘅字母<br />\nA, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, M, N, O, P, S, T, U, W, Y<br />\n咪就係英文字母囉<br />\n名都係叫返ABCD咁<br />\n不過就冇Q，R，V，X，Z<br />\n冇Q，X，Z係避免同K，S，J重覆<br />\n雖然我知佢哋唔係完全一樣<br />\n不過盡量從簡<br />\n冇R係粵語冇捲脷音<br />\n冇V係因為粵語冇呢種發音加上易同F或W混淆（我講自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n然後就係發音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲字母名還名<br />\n但用喺上嚟都要有代表嘅發音<br />\n除咗I同Y一樣外<br />\n一字一音，唔會好似英文咁個E有時係eh有時yi唔知開邊範<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA (ah), B (bi), C (tsi), D (di), E (eh), F (fi), G (hard G:gi 嘰), H (hee), I (yi), J (ji), K (ki), L (li), M (mi), N (ni), O (short O 屙), P (pi), S (si), T (ti), U (oo), W (wi), Y (yi)<br />\n拼寫基本上採用耶魯方案<br />\n但不寫Ch只寫C代表冇送氣聲<br />\nC不發S或K音<br />\nca&ne;ka, ce&ne;se, ci&ne;si, co&ne;ko, cu&ne;ku<br />\n係差、車、痴、搓、處（呢個係cyu）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於係基於粵語所以都係六個聲調<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用keyboard試咗好耐啲符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發覺啲字母能配搭嘅符號不一<br />\n兼好難用一種keyboard出晒咁多種符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以呢個部份同現實國際音標完全唔同<br />\n純粹9吹（根本成篇都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n暫時未諗到更好方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一聲：a, e, i, o, u 一無標音<br />\n第二聲：&auml;, &euml;, &iuml;, &ouml;, &uuml; 二兩點<br />\n第三聲：&aacute;, &eacute;, &iacute;, &oacute;, &uacute; 三上 <span class=\"small\">悠亞</span><br />\n第四聲：&agrave;, &egrave;, &igrave;, &ograve;, &ugrave; 四落<br />\n第五聲：&acirc;, &ecirc;, &icirc;, &ocirc;, &ucirc; 五拱<br />\n第六聲：ā, ē, ī, ō, ū 六直<br />\n<br />\n標音落喺第一個母音度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫起上嚟就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nseung 雙人<br />\ns&euml;ung 想念<br />\ns&eacute;ung 相片<br />\ns&egrave;ung 常識<br />\ns&ecirc;ung 上課<br />\nsēung 尚且<br />\n特例：ng, ṅg, ńg, ǹg, nĝ, nḡ<br />\n（n同g都配唔到兩點冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n組句方法好似英文咁詞與詞之間隔一個空位<br />\n句首同人稱代名詞第一個字母大楷<br />\nNg&ocirc; y&ucirc; N&ecirc;i<br />\n我與你<br />\n<br />\n變晒做字母後成堆雞腸都幾難搵到重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以加個規則嚟分辨動詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等一眼就睇到句子入面係做緊咩動作<br />\n如果嗰個字係以動詞性質出現<br />\n轉一轉寫個韻尾嚟表示佢係動詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-p, -t, -k時清濁音互換<br />\n拾 sāp -&gt; sāb<br />\n食 sīk -&gt; sīg<br />\n撥 p&uacute;t -&gt; p&uacute;d<br />\n<br />\n單個母音-a, -e, -i, -o, -u時補h<br />\n打 d&auml; -&gt; d&auml;h<br />\n射 sē -&gt; sēh<br />\n知 ji -&gt; jih<br />\n坐 c&ocirc; -&gt; c&ocirc;h<br />\n護 wū -&gt; wūh<br />\n<br />\n-ai, -ei, -oi, -ui時i轉y<br />\n睇 t&auml;i -&gt; t&auml;y<br />\n飛 fei -&gt; fey<br />\n採 c&ouml;i -&gt; c&ouml;y<br />\n陪 p&ugrave;i -&gt; p&ugrave;y<br />\n<br />\n-au, -eu, -iu, -ou時u轉w<br />\n扭 n&auml;u -&gt; n&auml;w<br />\n鋸 g&eacute;u -&gt; g&eacute;w<br />\n挑 tiu -&gt; tiw<br />\n告 g&oacute;u -&gt; g&oacute;w<br />\n<br />\n-n, -m, -ng時補n<br />\n問 mān -&gt; mānn<br />\n禁 gam -&gt; gamn<br />\n等 d&auml;ng -&gt; d&auml;nng<br />\n<br />\n雖然想一切從簡但搞搞下都幾複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有字都隔位嘅話整整下就全部散收收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以參考一下前綴用法去將一整個意思合返做一隻字<br />\n<br />\nbat-、ǹg-，表示相反意思<br />\n不少 bats&iuml;u<br />\n唔好 ǹgh&ouml;u<br />\n<br />\nh&ouml;u-、ciu-、g&iacute;ng-，表示更高程度<br />\n好大 h&ouml;udāai<br />\n超多 ciudo<br />\n勁細 g&iacute;ngs&aacute;i<br />\n<br />\n最難搞就係tense<br />\n有諗過後綴，但都係分返開用嚟識別時態好似好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nj&ouml;表示過去或完成狀態<br />\n做咗 jōw j&ouml;<br />\n<br />\ngw&oacute;表示經驗<br />\n去過 h&eacute;uy gw&oacute;<br />\n<br />\n搞咁耐到底用喺上嚟係點嘅呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係應用例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGamyāt Ng&ocirc; s&euml;unng h&eacute;uy gaai<br />\n今日 我 想 去 街<br />\nN&eacute;i gamyāt y&auml;mn j&ouml; mēi?<br />\n你 今日 飲 咗 未？<br />\nS&eacute;unng l&igrave;ndang māt yīngjan<br />\n上 連登 勿 認真<br />\n<br />\n同音字打算用異拼解決但未諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇學過phonetic之類嘅嘢<br />\n我只係嚟詼諧下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變到越南文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講<br />\nGwonngfūg Heungg&ouml;ng s&igrave;dōi g&aacute;akmīng<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bc6cd7c195a2c71e6de87578b36049a437198e","tid":2142329,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6069fb02f0a3c6baa6cb8a2a7b5a617217613862","tid":2142329,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n見有人討論有關漢字拉丁化嘅嘢<br />\n講真現實可行程度都幾低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上亦有人講<br />\n不如直接用英文重實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（講得好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n但作為一種想像好似都幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設一個異世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫Honkongia<br />\n使用一種叫Honkongish嘅語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先介紹一下Honkongish嘅字母<br />\nA, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, M, N, O, P, S, T, U, W, Y<br />\n咪就係英文字母囉<br />\n名都係叫返ABCD咁<br />\n不過就冇Q，R，V，X，Z<br />\n冇Q，X，Z係避免同K，S，J重覆<br />\n雖然我知佢哋唔係完全一樣<br />\n不過盡量從簡<br />\n冇R係粵語冇捲脷音<br />\n冇V係因為粵語冇呢種發音加上易同F或W混淆（我講自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n然後就係發音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲字母名還名<br />\n但用喺上嚟都要有代表嘅發音<br />\n除咗I同Y一樣外<br />\n一字一音，唔會好似英文咁個E有時係eh有時yi唔知開邊範<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA (ah), B (bi), C (tsi), D (di), E (eh), F (fi), G (hard G:gi 嘰), H (hee), I (yi), J (ji), K (ki), L (li), M (mi), N (ni), O (short O 屙), P (pi), S (si), T (ti), U (oo), W (wi), Y (yi)<br />\n拼寫基本上採用耶魯方案<br />\n但不寫Ch只寫C代表冇送氣聲<br />\nC不發S或K音<br />\nca&ne;ka, ce&ne;se, ci&ne;si, co&ne;ko, cu&ne;ku<br />\n係差、車、痴、搓、處（呢個係cyu）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於係基於粵語所以都係六個聲調<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用keyboard試咗好耐啲符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發覺啲字母能配搭嘅符號不一<br />\n兼好難用一種keyboard出晒咁多種符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以呢個部份同現實國際音標完全唔同<br />\n純粹9吹（根本成篇都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n暫時未諗到更好方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一聲：a, e, i, o, u 一無標音<br />\n第二聲：&auml;, &euml;, &iuml;, &ouml;, &uuml; 二兩點<br />\n第三聲：&aacute;, &eacute;, &iacute;, &oacute;, &uacute; 三上 <span class=\"small\">悠亞</span><br />\n第四聲：&agrave;, &egrave;, &igrave;, &ograve;, &ugrave; 四落<br />\n第五聲：&acirc;, &ecirc;, &icirc;, &ocirc;, &ucirc; 五拱<br />\n第六聲：ā, ē, ī, ō, ū 六直<br />\n<br />\n標音落喺第一個母音度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫起上嚟就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nseung 雙人<br />\ns&euml;ung 想念<br />\ns&eacute;ung 相片<br />\ns&egrave;ung 常識<br />\ns&ecirc;ung 上課<br />\nsēung 尚且<br />\n特例：ng, ṅg, ńg, ǹg, nĝ, nḡ<br />\n（n同g都配唔到兩點冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n組句方法好似英文咁詞與詞之間隔一個空位<br />\n句首同人稱代名詞第一個字母大楷<br />\nNg&ocirc; y&ucirc; N&ecirc;i<br />\n我與你<br />\n<br />\n變晒做字母後成堆雞腸都幾難搵到重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以加個規則嚟分辨動詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等一眼就睇到句子入面係做緊咩動作<br />\n如果嗰個字係以動詞性質出現<br />\n轉一轉寫個韻尾嚟表示佢係動詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-p, -t, -k時清濁音互換<br />\n拾 sāp -&gt; sāb<br />\n食 sīk -&gt; sīg<br />\n撥 p&uacute;t