ji\" /><br />\n冇學過phonetic之類嘅嘢<br />\n我只係嚟詼諧下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變到越南文咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講<br />\nGwonngfūg Heungg&ouml;ng s&igrave;dōi g&aacute;akmīng<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"我剩係睇最後都知講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />習總is watching you"},{"pid":"3aa967331d46ba8510e8b9b2c34fab0af30d53e4","tid":2142329,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"擇言？"},{"pid":"e323d5a4571e3c6e05520de26181601e5640ec39","tid":2142329,"uid":38801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"差唔多同越南文一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果要將廣東話拼音化<br />\n用注音或者平假名咁樣嘅文字<br />\n甚至諺文咁樣嘅款嘅 <br />\n可能會好過用拉丁文<br />\n唔知點解感覺上用拉丁文唔係幾美觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68030baf1c3506af4d79bd467da6ee58913b9ef","tid":2142329,"uid":171157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"唔係好明但玩得幾有心機，幫你推下"},{"pid":"f82238656050a84c1d2e800ec09052e1e4fe577c","tid":2142329,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"當年韓國世宗大王搞既訓民正音其實係點？<br />\n有無得借鏡？<br />\n<br />\nBtw如果漢字拉丁化<br />\n中國會更易解體<br />\n因為雖然少左人講，但都有方言存在<br />\n聽過話當時史大林都想將漢字拉丁化<br />\n原因正正就係想中國解體。<br />\n睇返當年中華蘇維埃共和國憲法都睇得出史大林有咁既意圖。<br />\n<br />\n同埋聽過有人話廣東話或者中文其實不利利學發展，唔知係唔係真。<br />\n<br />\n利伸 純粹廢up"},{"pid":"1e8af14c1127adcdc4f2adee861ed5d9b6cf24bd","tid":2142329,"uid":363330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e323d